    "ideation": "The Eye emoji should feel like an all-seeing, omnipresent observer—conscious but non-human. The acting choice is to treat the face as a single cosmic ocular organ. I am using asymmetry to create a sense of mechanical or mystical scanning: the two robot eyes will operate independently to suggest one 'larger' eye's depth or a complex sensor array. The arc moves from wide-eyed curiosity to a pinpoint 'aperture' focus, followed by a rapid, unblinking saccade (mechanical scanning), and finally a slow, heavy dilation. The mouth represents the visual signal processing: starting as a flat line and evolving into a complex, high-frequency data wave as the eye 'sees' more. Color transitions from observation-blue to analysis-violet and finally a deep, omniscient white-teal.",
